Package net.croz.nrich.registry.starter.properties

Record Class NrichRegistryProperties

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Record
net.croz.nrich.registry.starter.properties.NrichRegistryProperties
Record Components:
defaultReadOnlyPropertyList - List of property names that should always be marked as readonly.
registrySearch - Registry search configuration used by DefaultStringToTypeConverter.
defaultConverterEnabled - Whether default string to type converter (DefaultStringToTypeConverter) used for converting strings to property values when searching registry is enabled.
defaultJavaToJavascriptConverterEnabled - Whether default Java to Javascript type converter (DefaultJavaToJavascriptTypeConverter) used for converting Java to Javascript types is enabled.
configurationEndpointPath - Endpoint path of RegistryConfigurationController
dataEndpointPath - Endpoint path of RegistryDataController
enumEndpointPath - Endpoint path of RegistryEnumController
historyEndpointPath - Endpoint path of RegistryHistoryController
registryConfiguration - Registry configuration used for defining entities and groups which will be managed.
@ConfigurationProperties("nrich.registry") public record NrichRegistryProperties(List<String> defaultReadOnlyPropertyList, @NestedConfigurationProperty NrichRegistryProperties.RegistrySearchProperties registrySearch, boolean defaultConverterEnabled, boolean defaultJavaToJavascriptConverterEnabled, String configurationEndpointPath, String dataEndpointPath, String enumEndpointPath, String historyEndpointPath, @NestedConfigurationProperty RegistryConfiguration registryConfiguration) extends Record
